{"tid":1550843,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"工人姐姐plan","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T13:58:28.000Z","uid":261184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f84ae4cfa8d80e108fc9325b530f80920aca0c6f","tid":1550843,"uid":261184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":35,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:03:22.000Z","msg":"請介紹"},{"pid":"4a7c76f7a36d3749002cb1635300d3a6b5fbf775","tid":1550843,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"627cdbe61485a9dc529d70c4afda189ef373c656","tid":1550843,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:03:46.000Z","msg":"試下中英都跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"a2c641b63f4827a4794c0a2a37664e2fbd3b97cc","tid":1550843,"uid":226392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9d751ed3d00f6b863a7fde4b1175712ff45d824","tid":1550843,"uid":225880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:04:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d03be196242176728b6ca4dc7c459d4658f47701","tid":1550843,"uid":228984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:05:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91e9854f22a2411d5f5a7c332cb8bd0272b140b5","tid":1550843,"uid":226731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:07:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3217b7d503645585ea74d78cbc3fae58dd3bf0f2","tid":1550843,"uid":173831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:27:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94072cc66a33de9d422f08b7edbfaed0c062649c","tid":1550843,"uid":252546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:10:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36df8bcb5421924fd6147753fb2b16cc8cbd554f","tid":1550843,"uid":67461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:22:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43a64a99ba6c7d94